title: Rigmar Radio Karaoke Collection 33800
description:
UK and Europe Peers may notice that there is a huge amount of Country and Western Karaoke in this collection.   That is due to the fact I lived in Timmins Ontario for 6 years where Country and Western is huge, as indeed it is of course all over North America.   I am aware that is not the case in Europe.  Sorry about this.

300 More CDG+MP3 Songs from the Rigmar Radio working Karaoke collection.

Rigmar Radio - Rockin' the Free World since 1967
